    <summary>Lightweight monitoring adapter for Glances + Uptime Kuma</summary>
    <description>
GlanceWatch is a lightweight monitoring adapter that connects Glances (system monitoring) with Uptime Kuma (alerting platform).

Features:
- Real-time system metrics (CPU, RAM, Disk)
- Configurable thresholds
- Web UI with live status
- REST API for Uptime Kuma integration
- Automatic service management
- System health monitoring (uptime, load average, network stats)

Requirements:
- Python 3.8 or higher
- Glances running on localhost:61208
    </description>
